# Only ship the rolling Mindflow-latest.dmg.
# Versioned DMGs (Mindflow-X.Y.Z.dmg) and any Meetflow-* legacy artifacts
# bloat the repo and aren't referenced by VERSION.json (the auto-updater
# always points at Mindflow-latest.dmg). Local copies stay on disk during
# the release flow; git just doesn't track them.
Mindflow-*.dmg
!Mindflow-latest.dmg
Meetflow-*.dmg

.DS_Store
